She turned and walked to Destructor.  She whispered to him, "That 
will have to wait untill our guests have left. Right now I have to 
deal with Cyber Claw standing there at the entrance and Black Aracnia 
will be here soon.  After they have left, we shall finish that 
project. Now, will you stand with me here while I wait for Black 
Aracnia to arrive? When she get's here, I would appreciate you 
standing by me.  I might need you in case of trouble." She smiled at 
him and then turned and faced CyberClaw.  She took a few steps close 
to the newcomer. "Would you like me to call Aracnia to make sure 
everything is alright. As you said, you are early, can I get you any 
refreshment?"
